          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The thick target inverse kinematic method",
                "was applied to the study of isobaric analog state in",
                "the neutron-rich nucleus Li-9. For this purpose, an",
                "excitation function for He-8+p elastic scattering was",
                "measured in the center-of-momentum energy range from",
                " 1.6 to 5.8 MeV. Three T=5/2 states in Li-9(isobaric",
                "analogs of He-9) were observed."
              ]
            }
          ],
